data.description: Welcome to your tastefully updated rambler in the friendly Evergreen Prairie neighborhood. The open floorplan places all entertaining spaces at the front of the home, with all three bedrooms towards the back for privacy. Efficient kitchen includes newer SS appliances, including smart LG ThinQ dishwasher. Dining room offers slider access to back patio for indoor/outdoor gatherings. Primary bedroom includes en suite half bath. Recent energy efficient updates include tankless hot water heater, HardiePlank siding, gutters, windows & insulation. Trane heat pump for energy efficient heating & cooling. Fully fenced back yard with hot tub offers space & privacy. Easy commute to JBLM, easy freeway access, and city transit. Yelm School District.
